summary.description:
Today, a bit warmer for the feels like temperature (up 3.2°C) and outside temperature (up 2.5°C) and more moisture-laden outside humidity (up 8%) and rainfall (up 1.1 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in pressure (up 9 mbar) and cloud levels (up 543 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in feels like temperature (up 38.7°C), outside temperature (up 40.8°C), dew point temperature (up 36.0°C), and cloud levels (up 949 m) when compared to today.
